_:N104aad99941b42b1a5651713400dce25 <http://schema.org/name> "Procurement at Nuclear Waste Services" .
_:N44afc9cd70ba482a957329eb3894bb5a <http://schema.org/sameAs> <https://www.gov.uk/environment/radioactive-and-nuclear-substances-and-waste> .
